info.description: This is the public Twilio REST API.
info.title: Twilio - Api

get.description: Retrieves a collection of Accounts belonging to the account used to make the request

parameters.description: Only return the Account resources with friendly names that exactly match this name.
parameters.name: FriendlyName

parameters.description: Only return Account resources with the given status. Can be `closed`, `suspended` or `active`.
parameters.name: Status

parameters.description: How many resources to return in each list page. The default is 50, and the maximum is 1000.
parameters.name: PageSize

post.description: Create a new Twilio Subaccount from the account making the request

FriendlyName.description: A human readable description of the account to create, defaults to `SubAccount Created at {YYYY-MM-DD HH:MM meridian}`
